    "They can enable real-time odor detection and manipulation, which is valuable for health diagnostics, such as detecting diseases through scent biomarkers.",
    "Overall, these studies show the promise of AI in overcoming challenges in olfactory research and improving both precision and applicability.",
    "Despite these promising developments, a persistent challenge in olfactory AI research lies in the lack of standardized, high-quality datasets.",
